data.description: Listed $10,000.00 below appraisal value. This charming 3 bedroom, 3 bath home is a hidden gem nestled by the serene waters of Church Branch on a .76 acre lot. The main floor features 1 bedroom & 1 bath, family room, kitchen, laundry room & back porch. The 2nd floor features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, a kitchenette and a flex room that would be perfect for guest, teenagers, gym, game room or whatever suits your life style. This house offers the potential to create your dream lakeside retreat with a touch of personal updates and customization. Home being sold as is. Home inspection available for buyer review. Seller to give $5000.00 at closing for paint, flooring, etc. Fenced in side yard. America's Preferred Home Warranty included on property.
